<title>CHINA: Shanghai Petro halt for rights issue.</title>
<headline>Shanghai Petro halt for rights issue.</headline>
<dateline>SHANGHAI 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shanghai Petrochemical Co said in a statement on Friday that it requested the exchange to suspend trading of its A shares in Shanghai for half a day after an announcement of an H share rights issue.  </p>
<p>The company announced earlier today that it would place 500 million H shares globally at HK$2.075 each.</p>
<p>&quot;Due to this announcement, the board of director asked the (Shanghai) exchange to suspend trading in the company's shares for half a day,&quot; the statement said.</p>
<p>On Thursday the company's A share closed at 4.28 yuan.</p>
